subsection.def:
by-election (補選)
                has the meaning assigned to it by section 3(1) of the Legislative Council
                Ordinance (Cap. 542);

paragraph.content:
in relation to a geographical constituency—a person who is nominated to
                        be returned as a Member for that geographical constituency at a general
                        election or by-election;

subsection.def:
Member (議員) has the
                meaning assigned to it by section 3(1) of the Legislative Council
                Ordinance (Cap. 542);
